<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #1a4d7a; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .footer { background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
        .success { color: #28a745; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }
        .details { background-color: white; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>결제 완료 안내</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>안녕하세요 {{name}},</p>
            <p class="success">✓ 결제가 완료되었습니다.</p>
            <div class="details">
                <h3>결제 상세</h3>
                <p><strong>거래번호:</strong> {{transactionId}}</p>
                <p><strong>결제금액:</strong> {{amount}}</p>
                <p><strong>결제일시:</strong> {{paidAt}}</p>
                <p><strong>대출계좌:</strong> {{accountNumber}}</p>
            </div>
            <p>결제 내용을 확인하시려면 대시보드를 방문해주세요.</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button" style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
                    대시보드 보기
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2026 Fiscus. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>이 이메일은 자동 발송되었습니다.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>